INSERT INTO `course` VALUES (1,1,'Basic Etiquette and Grooming',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Basic-Etiquette-and-Grooming-Hindi_basic.jpg','Etiquette and Grooming are an integral part of one\'s personality. They create awareness of the importance of soft skills and first impressions. They sharpen an employee\'s professional image and increases their self-confidence, motivation, commitment and positive morale leading to greater performance and productivity. Our basic program on Etiquette and Grooming, will help people looking for jobs, be better at an interview, at making a sale and making a positive impression who whoever they interact with at work. It will also help them stay fit and attractive and have good relationships in their personal life.',1,'Active',0,'Basic-Etiquette-and-Grooming','','','','',''),(2,1,'Basic Etiquette and Grooming (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Basic-Etiquette-and-Grooming-Hindi_basic.jpg','Etiquette and Grooming are an integral part of one\'s personality. They create awareness of the importance of soft skills and first impressions. They sharpen an employee\'s professional image and increases their self-confidence, motivation, commitment and positive morale leading to greater performance and productivity. Our basic program on Etiquette and Grooming, will help people looking for jobs, be better at an interview, at making a sale and making a positive impression who whoever they interact with at work. It will also help them stay fit and attractive and have good relationships in their personal life.',2,'Active',0,'2','This is meta description','This is meta keywords','{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n \"@type\": \"VideoObject\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Creative Thinking Skills Course\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Creative Thinking Skills Course Module:\r\nModule 1: Introduction to Creative Thinking Skills\r\nModule 2: What is Creative Thinking Skill?\r\nModule 3: Need for Creative Thinking Skills\r\nModule 4: Process for Creative Thinking Skills\r\nModule 5: How to encourage Creative Thinking\r\n \r\nQuiz\",\r\n \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/2-2.jpg\",\r\n \"uploadDate\": \"\",\r\n \"duration\": \"PT0M0S\",  \r\n \"publisher\": {\r\n \"@type\": \"Organization\",\r\n \"name\": \"Train2Sucess\",\r\n \"logo\": {\r\n  \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\r\n \"url\": \"https://train2success.in/assets/img/logo.png\",\r\n \"width\": ,\r\n \"height\":\r\n  }\r\n  },\r\n  \"potentialAction\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"SeekToAction\",\r\n    \"target\": \"https://train2success.in/courses/details/creative-thinking-skills/={seek_to_second_number}\",\r\n    \"startOffset-input\": \"required name=seek_to_second_number\"\r\n  }\r\n}','Basic Etiquette and Grooming (Hindi)','This is meta author'),(3,1,'Being Interviewed',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Being-Interviewed_b-1.jpg','Everyone who desires to have a career is being interviewed by someone. The purpose of the interview is to understand if interviewed person is eligible for the job or not but that is not the single motive. The person being interviewed is also tested for his ethics, manners, politeness. This video helps them to understand how can you prepare for your next interview to make a good impression.',3,'Active',0,'Course Tag / URL','','','','',''),(4,1,'Being Interviewed (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Being-Interviewed_b-1.jpg','Everyone who desires to have a career is being interviewed by someone. The purpose of the interview is to understand if interviewed person is eligible for the job or not but that is not the single motive. The person being interviewed is also tested for his ethics, manners, politeness. This video helps them to understand how can you prepare for your next interview to make a good impression.',4,'Active',0,'4','','','','',''),(5,1,'Creative Thinking',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Creative-Thinking.jpg','In this highly competitive world where ideas are at the peak, it is a pre-requisite that one must be able to adapt and think for new and creative ideas. This video will help you in this process and within a few minutes you will be on your way to exploring your creative side and will be able to come up with new and bright ideas!',5,'Active',0,'5','','','','',''),(6,1,'Creative Thinking (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Creative-Thinking.jpg','In this highly competitive world where ideas are at the peak, it is a pre-requisite that one must be able to adapt and think for new and creative ideas. This video will help you in this process and within a few minutes you will be on your way to exploring your creative side and will be able to come up with new and bright ideas!',6,'Active',0,'6','','','','',''),(7,1,'Customer Relationship Management',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Customer-relationship-management_B.jpg','If Customer is King, then Customer Relationship Management is the hidden secret to keep the King happy. In today\'s world we have so many interactions with different sets of clients. Through this snippet you will be able to understand how effectively you can maintain your CRM and make all your customers your best customers.',7,'Active',0,'7','','','','',''),(8,1,'Customer Relationship Management (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Customer-relationship-management_B.jpg','If Customer is King, then Customer Relationship Management is the hidden secret to keep the King happy. In today\'s world we have so many interactions with different sets of clients. Through this snippet you will be able to understand how effectively you can maintain your CRM and make all your customers your best customers.',8,'Active',0,'8','','','','',''),(9,1,'Goal Setting',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-8-600x360.jpg','Everybody has goals in his/her life. But do we carry out the task of setting Goals and how to go about achieving the goals. If we have bigger goals then we need to set smaller goals to get the bigger goal near us and achieve that. This video will help you in goal setting, probably the biggest and the most important aspect of our life.',9,'Active',0,'9','','','','',''),(10,1,'Goal Setting (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-8-600x360.jpg','Everybody has goals in his/her life. But do we carry out the task of setting Goals and how to go about achieving the goals. If we have bigger goals then we need to set smaller goals to get the bigger goal near us and achieve that. This video will help you in goal setting, probably the biggest and the most important aspect of our life.',10,'Active',0,'10','','','','',''),(11,1,'Handling Rejections',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Handling-rejection_basic.jpg','Rejection is a part of life and the earlier we understand it, the better it is for us. Rejection can be difficult to deal with. More difficult to deal with is the Depression & anxiety of getting rejected. This video will give you pointer on how you can handle rejection and move forward & start looking for new opportunities.',11,'Active',0,'11','','','','',''),(12,1,'Handling Rejections (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Handling-rejection_basic.jpg','Rejection is a part of life and the earlier we understand it, the better it is for us. Rejection can be difficult to deal with. More difficult to deal with is the Depression & anxiety of getting rejected. This video will give you pointer on how you can handle rejection and move forward & start looking for new opportunities.',12,'Active',0,'12','','','','',''),(13,1,'Making Meetings Work',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Making-Meetings-Work_basic.jpg','Meetings are critical and a necessary part of every business irrespective of sectors. Meetings while they could prove to be game changers for a business, they could even end up wasting precious man hours of everyone involved directly or indirectly. This video will help you understand some aspects of meetings so as to make them work for you and your business. These tips could prove to bring out the maximum from every meeting, strategically and decisively.',13,'Active',0,'13','','','','',''),(14,1,'Negotiation Skills',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Negotiation-Skills-1.jpg','Negotiation skills are qualities that allow two or more parties to reach a compromise. These are often soft skills and include abilities such as communication, persuasion, planning, strategizing and cooperating. Negotiations occur frequently within the workplace, between co-workers or between an employee and employer. They are skills that you will require depending on your environment, your desired outcome and the parties involved. Our basic program on Negotiation skills will help you understand the basics of negotiating effectively, to your benefit and in turn help you to develop your career, secure a higher salary and meet crucial business needs.',14,'Active',0,'14','','','','',''),(15,1,'Negotiation Skills (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Negotiation-Skills-1.jpg','Negotiation skills are qualities that allow two or more parties to reach a compromise. These are often soft skills and include abilities such as communication, persuasion, planning, strategizing and cooperating. Negotiations occur frequently within the workplace, between co-workers or between an employee and employer. They are skills that you will require depending on your environment, your desired outcome and the parties involved. Our basic program on Negotiation skills will help you understand the basics of negotiating effectively, to your benefit and in turn help you to develop your career, secure a higher salary and meet crucial business needs.',15,'Active',0,'15','','','','',''),(16,1,'Positive Attitude',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Positive-Attitude.jpg','Having a positive attitude means being optimistic about situations, interactions, people and yourself. People with positive attitudes remain hopeful and see the best even in difficult situations and this makes it easier to avoid worries and negative thinking. A positive attitude makes you happier, it improves your relationships, and it even increases your chances of success and can help you to make better decisions. Some studies show that people with a positive attitude live longer. Our basic program on Positive Attitude, will guide you towards making positive thinking a habit, and making the best out of any situation you find yourself in.',16,'Active',0,'16','','','','',''),(17,1,'Positive Attitude (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Positive-Attitude.jpg','Having a positive attitude means being optimistic about situations, interactions, people and yourself. People with positive attitudes remain hopeful and see the best even in difficult situations and this makes it easier to avoid worries and negative thinking. A positive attitude makes you happier, it improves your relationships, and it even increases your chances of success and can help you to make better decisions. Some studies show that people with a positive attitude live longer. Our basic program on Positive Attitude, will guide you towards making positive thinking a habit, and making the best out of any situation you find yourself in.',17,'Active',0,'17','','','','',''),(18,1,'Productivity Tips',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/productivity-tips_b.jpg','Productivity defines the success of a person at his workplace and also in life. One must strive to be productive as much as they can, so they lead a good life and a healthy one as well as a wealthy one. This video will help you increase your productivity with simple tips that may not seem a lot, but if you add them together and follow them religiously, you will see a change around in your life.',18,'Active',0,'18','','','','',''),(19,1,'Productivity Tips (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/productivity-tips_b.jpg','Productivity defines the success of a person at his workplace and also in life. One must strive to be productive as much as they can, so they lead a good life and a healthy one as well as a wealthy one. This video will help you increase your productivity with simple tips that may not seem a lot, but if you add them together and follow them religiously, you will see a change around in your life.',19,'Active',0,'19','','','','',''),(20,1,'Systematic Working',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Capture.jpg','Systematic working is described as something that is done according to a system, in an orderly, methodical way. Someone who systematically records her dreams, is careful to write them in a notebook every single morning. A systematic working approach is often used at the workplace. The goal of this approach is to identify the most efficient means of generating consistent and optimum results. It is also important to know the purpose and the objectives as these will be used as their basis in achieving the company\'s goals.',20,'Active',0,'20','','','','',''),(21,1,'Systematic Working (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Capture.jpg','Systematic working is described as something that is done according to a system, in an orderly, methodical way. Someone who systematically records her dreams, is careful to write them in a notebook every single morning. A systematic working approach is often used at the workplace. The goal of this approach is to identify the most efficient means of generating consistent and optimum results. It is also important to know the purpose and the objectives as these will be used as their basis in achieving the company\'s goals.',21,'Active',0,'21','','','','',''),(22,1,'Telephonic Skills',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Telephone-Skills-1.jpg','Effective telephone skills are very much important, be it workplace, at home or even with friends. Active listening is also an essential area and this video will help you to respond effectively, communicate well, take messages correctly, putting people on hold and much more. Take some quick notes and improve your skills.',22,'Active',0,'22','','','','',''),(23,1,'Telephonic Skills (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Telephone-Skills-2.jpg','Effective telephone skills are very much important, be it workplace, at home or even with friends. Active listening is also an essential area and this video will help you to respond effectively, communicate well, take messages correctly, putting people on hold and much more. Take some quick notes and improve your skills.',23,'Active',0,'23','','','','',''),(24,1,'The Joy of Diversity',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/The-Joy-of-Diversity.jpg','We as humans are diversified into gender, race, caste, religion and if we all live our life with peace & humanity, we will be the epitome of diversified culture. The joy of diversity is about live & let live so we all can have peace. This video explains the joy living with diversified cultures all being a part of our life.',24,'Active',0,'24','','','','',''),(25,1,'The Joy of Diversity (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/The-Joy-of-Diversity.jpg','We as humans are diversified into gender, race, caste, religion and if we all live our life with peace & humanity, we will be the epitome of diversified culture. The joy of diversity is about live & let live so we all can have peace. This video explains the joy living with diversified cultures all being a part of our life.',25,'Active',0,'25','','','','',''),(26,1,'Time Management',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Time-management.jpg','They don\'t manufacture time so managing time is the most important aspect of our lives. We say time flies by, but actually we are so busy running our lives that we forget to manage time. This video will help you make the most of your time and will give you pointers to do so.',26,'Active',0,'26','','','','',''),(27,1,'Time Management (Hindi)',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Time-management.jpg','They don\'t manufacture time so managing time is the most important aspect of our lives. We say time flies by, but actually we are so busy running our lives that we forget to manage time. This video will help you make the most of your time and will give you pointers to do so.',27,'Active',0,'27','','','','',''),(28,2,'Being Interviewed',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/2-4.jpg','Everyone invariably goes through this phase where he/she is expected to show her skills, to get a job for themselves. If not a job interview, even a client presentation could be an interview to get the deal and a lot more situations that don\'t necessarily stand as job interviews but are situations where you need to show up on time, and impress the person across the table. This course will show you, how to be prepared, types of interviews, preparations and more.',28,'Active',0,'28','','','','',''),(29,2,'Change Management',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/3-1.jpg','Change is the only constant and evolution is proof. Everything is dynamic, and what was in style or demand yesterday, may not be tomorrow. So what can we do? What we must do is prepare for change, accept it, and get ahead by being the early birds in implementing what\'s new. This is what this course is all about. What is change, why is it important and how can we use change to power up our careers, life and overall existence as a whole.',32,'Active',0,'Change-Management','Learn about change management in depth. Know why change management is important for your organization. Click to learn more!\r\n',' change management, change management course, manage change, organizational change management, designing change\r\n','','',''),(30,2,'Creative Thinking',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/2-2.jpg','Creative thinking is an analysis and evaluation of an idea or a situation with an open mind to find new ways for problem solving.',38,'Active',0,'30','','','','',''),(31,2,'Customer Relationship Management',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/3.jpg','',43,'Active',0,'31','','','','',''),(32,2,'Customer Service',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-4.jpg','In an age where every customer is important for every business, excelling in Customer Service is essential for every business to survive and thrive. So, this course will walk you through with identifying the customer, his / her needs and delivering excellent service and ensuring that the customer stays satisfied and definitely returns back for more products / services. Through this course, every sales person or a back-end customer service executive will get an insight into the customers mind, thinking from his shoes so as to deliver the best possible service. If you interact with your customers in any format, this is a must for you.',50,'Active',0,'32','','','','',''),(33,2,'Decision Making',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/2-1.jpg','It is never easy to make a tough decision, rather any decision for that matter. Sometimes it is said, that you need to trust your instinct and sometimes people follow a well outlined process that helps them analyze the entire situation and then come to a conclusion. This process of decision making is what you will learn in this course. There are also tools that will help you implement this action and you will also find those in this course. You don\'t have to be a big key decision maker to enroll for this course, even if you are starting out you will still have decisions to take, on your career, workplace and in life, so this is good to get you started in the right direction.',55,'Active',0,'33','','','','',''),(34,2,'Effective Communication',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/Effective-Communication-1.jpg','Are you struggling in communicating your thoughts to people at work at home? Do you want to get to a place where you are effectively able to convey your thoughts so as to get the desired outcome that you are wishing for? If you answered YES to either of the questions, then Effective Communications is the right course for you. We are always communicating with someone or the other. Physically, over the internet or any other form but we are in constant communication mode throughout the day. To be able to communicate effectively, one needs to know the different types of communications, it\'s necessary to bust some barriers that are holding you back, in fact listening is also a vital element of effective communication. Through this course, you will be taken through all these details to help you effectively communicate in whatever form you are conversating.',58,'Active',0,'34','','','','',''),(35,2,'Inventory Management',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/4.jpg','Inventory Management is an important function when there is an organization who makes physical products. Systematically managing inflow of products, stocking and outgo of products is Inventory Management. While it may sound very simple it can really be complex. This course will teach you various processes and techniques of Inventory Management, the purpose of the function and will make you better at the function. At difficult times if this function is not performed correctly can wreak havoc in any organization and that is what makes this role very vital in the smooth functioning of an organization engaged in physical products.',64,'Active',0,'35','','','','',''),(36,2,'Managing Executive Stress',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/2-3.jpg','With competition soaring and being at an all time high, it is evident that there will be some amount of stress to high levels of stress for executives at every level. Even if you are not having stress as on date, at some point of time, you will be faced with challenging situations, situations that will pile some or large amounts of stress on you, especially tough decisions. This course will help you understand stress, it\'s forms and how to manage it such that it doesn\'t cause any harm to you, physically or mentally',69,'Active',0,'36','','','','',''),(37,2,'People Skills for Executives',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-6.jpg','While we may say that we deal with organizations, in essentials it is people whom we interact with or deal with. So, without a doubt, people skills are of prime importance. Getting work done in your desired timelines is no easy task, especially in larger organizations where hierarchies and systems are in place. This is where your people skills will matter. Your rapport, your understanding and getting things done on time will be quite a game changer in your career if you get your people skills in place.',74,'Active',0,'37','','','','',''),(38,2,'Power of Thought',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1.jpg','What you think is what you become? A profound saying that holds true even today and will hold true forever. Just as exercise works your body and gets you in shape it also acts as a memory booster and the benefits that it provides your mind are endless, similarly the power of your thoughts are way beyond measure. This course will help you understand the mind body connection, how to visualize what you desire and how to introspect yourself.',78,'Active',0,'38','','','','',''),(39,2,'Presentation Skills',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-5.jpg','If you are an executive or a student doing a project and wish to get into the nuances of Improving your Presentation skills then this course is ideal for you. We all make presentations BUT at the last moment. Then we just dive into PowerPoint, pick up a template and start typing out the text without planning. But Presentation Skills is an art and if polished, it will make you more confident and you will be able to deliver great presentations that will certainly make your peers come to you and ask you how did you do what you did! PowerPoint is a tool that is used by every company or individual around us.',82,'Active',0,'39','','','','',''),(40,2,'Successful Marketing for Executives',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-1.jpg','Marketing is quite a skill of placing your product at the right place, right time and a lot more than that. But if one can master this art, then there is no stopping him or her from making a product into a global and iconic brand. This course will show you great amount of insights into what goes into successfully market your product and make it available at the right place for consumers to buy it.',98,'Active',0,'40','','','','',''),(41,2,'Telephone Skills',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/1-3.jpg','When you are sitting in front of a customer it is relatively easy to understand what he / she wants and offer a solution, but being behind a phone can be a little tricky. You don\'t get to see expressions, gestures, emotions and all that would ideally help you to judge the person sitting across. This course will help you with the nuances of Telephonic Skills that will help you understand the basics and address the challenges that come while managing conversations over a phone call. Taking messages, answering the call and a lot more of this is covered in this course.',103,'Active',0,'41','','','','',''),(42,1,'Effective Use of Social Media',0,'http://train2success.in/assets/images/course/effectively_use_social_media.jpg','Social media is a part of our lives, our personalities, our brands. Social media helps inform, amplify, connect, communicate, clarify, take decisions, provide aid, buy, sell, hire.\r\nEffective Use of Social Media is an easy-breezy ready reckoner for individuals, institutions, companies to know how to navigate the world of social media and which platform to use.',NULL,'Active',0,'42','','','','',''),(43,1,'Effective Use of Social Media(Hindi)',0,'http://train2success.in/assets/images/course/effectively_use_social_media_Hindi.jpg','Social media is a part of our lives, our personalities, our brands. Social media helps inform, amplify, connect, communicate, clarify, take decisions, provide aid, buy, sell, hire.\r\nEffective Use of Social Media is an easy-breezy ready reckoner for individuals, institutions, companies to know how to navigate the world of social media and which platform to use.',NULL,'Active',0,'43','','','','',''),(44,3,'demo course',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/af7cab.png','test',NULL,'Active',0,'44','','','','',''),(45,7,'tese course',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/a318e2.png','test course short description',NULL,'Active',0,'45','','','','',''),(46,8,'Test course',0,'https://train2success.in/assets/images/course/917a8f.jpg','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500',NULL,'Active',0,'46','','','','','');
